  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = failwith "to be implemented" in
    let base = failwith "to be implemeneted" in
    let args = [List.combine l1] in
    let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

  let leng2 = List.length l2 in
  (((clone 0 (leng2 - leng1)) @ l1), ((clone 0 (leng1 - leng2)) @ l2));;

let rec removeZero  : int list -> int list = fun l  -> 
  match l with | [] -> [] | h::t -> if h = 0 then removeZero t else l;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = failwith "to be implemented" in
    let base = failwith "to be implemeneted" in
    let args = [List.combine l1] in
    let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = failwith "to be implemented" in
    let base = failwith "to be implemeneted" in
    let args = [List.combine l1] in
    let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

    let f a x = x in
    let base = ([], []) in
    let args = [] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;
---------------------annofix------------------------
let rec clone x n = if n <= 0 then [] else x :: (clone x (n - 1));;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  let leng1 = List.length l1 in
  let leng2 = List.length l2 in
  (((clone 0 (leng2 - leng1)) @ l1), ((clone 0 (leng1 - leng2)) @ l2));;

914
---------------------bad------------------------
let pipe fs = let f a x = a x in let base = f in List.fold_left f base fs;;
--------------------fix-------------------------
let pipe fs =
  let f a x c = x (a c) in let base x = x in List.fold_left f base fs;;
-------------------anno bad--------------------------
let pipe  : ('a -> 'a) list -> ('a -> 'a) = fun fs  ->  let f a x = a x in let base = f in List.fold_left f base fs;;
---------------------annofix------------------------
let pipe  : ('a -> 'a) list -> ('a -> 'a) = fun fs  -> 
  let f a x c = x (a c) in let base x = x in List.fold_left f base fs;;

917
---------------------bad------------------------
let sqsum xs =
  let f a x sum x = sum + (x * x) in let base = 0 in List.fold_left f base xs;;

  let f a x = a + (x * x) in let base = 0 in List.fold_left f base xs;;

  let f a x sum x = sum + (x * x) in let base = 0 in List.fold_left f base xs;;

  let f a x = a + (x * x) in let base = 0 in List.fold_left f base xs;;

927
---------------------bad------------------------
let clone x n =
  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let x = padZero [9; 9] [1; 0; 0; 2];;

let clone x n =
  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero l =
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = match a with | (x1,x2)::xs -> (x1 + x2) :: x in
    let base = [] in
    let args = [] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

let l1 = [0; 0; 9; 9];;

let l2 = [1; 0; 0; 2];;

let x = (3, 3) :: (List.rev (List.combine l1 l2));;

let clone x n =
  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero l =
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd  : int list -> int list -> int list = fun l1 l2  -> 
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = [(0, [])] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

let bigAdd  : int list -> int list -> int list = fun l1 l2  -> 
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = [(0, [])] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

    let f a x = x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = [(0, [])] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

    let f a x = x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = [(0, [])] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in

    let f a x = a + x in

  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero l =
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = [(0, [])] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;
-------------------anno bad--------------------------

let x = (3, 3) :: (List.rev (List.combine l1 l2));;

let clone x n =
  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = match x with | (c,d::t) -> (c, a) in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = match l1 with | h::t -> [(h, (List.rev l2))] in
    let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;
--------------------fix-------------------------
let l1 = [0; 0; 9; 9];;

let l2 = [1; 0; 0; 2];;

let x = (3, 3) :: (List.rev (List.combine l1 l2));;

let clone x n =
  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)

    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero l =
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = match x with | (h1,h2)::t -> [h1 + h2] in
    let base = [] in
    let args = List.combine l1 l2 in
    let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;
--------------------fix-------------------------

let clone x n =
  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero l =
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = x in
    let base = [] in
    let args = [] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero l =
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd  : int list -> int list -> int list = fun l1 l2  -> 
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = match x with | (c,d::t) -> c + d in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = match l1 with | h::t -> [(h, l2)] in
    let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let l1 = [0; 0; 9; 9];;

let x = (3, 3) :: (List.rev (List.combine l1 l2));;

let clone x n =
  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero l =
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = [(0, [])] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;
-------------------anno bad--------------------------

  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = match x with | (d1,d2)::ds -> () in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = List.rev (List.combine l1 l2) in
    let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

    let base = (0, []) in

  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)

  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) acc =
    let f a x = match x with | (h1,h2)::t -> (h1 + h2) :: acc in
    let base = acc in
    let args = List.combine l1 l2 in
    let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2) []);;

  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = [((l1 + l2), [])] in
    let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero l =
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd  : int list -> int list -> int list = fun l1 l2  -> 
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = [(0, [])] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

let clone x n =
  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero l =
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = [(0, [])] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;
-------------------anno bad--------------------------

    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = List.rev (List.combine l1 l2) in

let bigAdd  : int list -> int list -> int list = fun l1 l2  -> 
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x =
      match a with | (c,(d1,d2)::ds) -> ((d1 + (d2 mod 10)), (d1 + d2)) in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = List.rev (List.combine l1 l2) in
    let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;
---------------------annofix------------------------
let l1 = [0; 0; 9; 9];;

let l2 = [1; 0; 0; 2];;

let x = (3, 3) :: (List.rev (List.combine l1 l2));;

let clone x n =
  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = [(0, [])] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

    let base = [l1] in
    let args = [(l1, l2)] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  (removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2)) 0 0 9 9) + (1 0 0 2);;

let l1 = [0; 0; 9; 9];;

let l2 = [1; 0; 0; 2];;

let x = (3, 3) :: (List.rev (List.combine l1 l2));;

let clone x n =
  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

    let base = (0, []) in

let clone x n =
  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero l =
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = [(0, [])] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;
-------------------anno bad--------------------------

    let args = [(0, [(l1, l2)])] in

  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero l =
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd  : int list -> int list -> int list = fun l1 l2  -> 
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = (a, a) in
    let base = [] in
    let args = l1 @ l2 in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;
---------------------annofix------------------------

  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = a + x in
    let base = [l1] in
    let args = [(l1, l2)] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  (removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2)) 0 0 9 9) + (1 0 0 2);;

let l2 = [1; 0; 0; 2];;

let clone x n =
  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero l =
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = a in
    let base = [] in
    let args = (l1, l2) in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero  : int list -> int list = fun l  -> 
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = [(0, [])] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

let rec removeZero l =
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = (0, l1) in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero  : int list -> int list = fun l  -> 
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = [(0, [])] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

let x = (3, 3) :: (List.rev (List.combine l1 l2));;

let clone x n =
  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero  : int list -> int list = fun l  -> 
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = (0, l1) in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;
---------------------annofix------------------------

    let f a x = x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = [(0, [])] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = match a with | (a1,a2)::aa -> (a1 + a2) :: x in
    let base = [] in
    let args = List.rev (List.combine l1 l2) in
    let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero l =
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = match x with | (c,d::t) -> (c, [a]) in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = match l1 with | h::t -> [(h, l2)] in
    let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;
--------------------fix-------------------------

let x = (3, 3) :: (List.rev (List.combine l1 l2));;

let clone x n =
  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let clone x n =
  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero l =
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = [(0, [])] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = match a with | (x1,x2)::xs -> (x1 + x2) :: x in
    let base = [] in
    let args = List.rev (List.combine l1 l2) in
    let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

let rec removeZero  : int list -> int list = fun l  -> 
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = [(0, [])] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

let clone x n =
  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let x = padZero [9; 9] [1; 0; 0; 2];;

let clone x n =
  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero  : int list -> int list = fun l  -> 
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) acc =
    let f a x = match x with | (h1,h2)::t -> (h1 + h2) :: acc in
    let base = acc in
    let args = List.combine l1 l2 in
    let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2) []);;
---------------------annofix------------------------

  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = [(0, [])] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero l =
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = match a with | (h1,h2)::t -> (h1 + h2) :: x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = List.rev (List.combine l1 l2) in
    let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;
--------------------fix-------------------------

let x = (3, 3) :: (List.rev (List.combine l1 l2));;

  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero  : int list -> int list = fun l  -> 
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = a + x in
    let base = [] in
    let args = [(l1, l2)] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  (removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2)) 0 0 9 9) + (1 0 0 2);;

let l1 = [0; 0; 9; 9];;

let l2 = [1; 0; 0; 2];;

let x = (3, 3) :: (List.rev (List.combine l1 l2));;

let clone x n =
  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero l =
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = x in
    let base = (0, []) in
    let args = [(0, [])] in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;
-------------------anno bad--------------------------

  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero  : int list -> int list = fun l  -> 
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = match x with | (q,w)::t -> (q + w) :: a | _ -> a in
    let base = [] in
    let args = List.combine l1 l2 in
    let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let x = padZero [9; 9] [1; 0; 0; 2];;

let clone x n =
  let rec helper x n acc =
    if n <= 0 then acc else helper x (n - 1) (x :: acc) in
  helper x n [];;

let padZero l1 l2 =
  if (List.length l1) < (List.length l2)
  then ((List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l2) - (List.length l1))) l1), l2)
  else (l1, (List.append (clone 0 ((List.length l1) - (List.length l2))) l2));;

let rec removeZero l =
  match l with | [] -> [] | x::xs -> if x = 0 then removeZero xs else x :: xs;;

let bigAdd l1 l2 =
  let add (l1,l2) =
    let f a x = a in
    let base = [] in
    let args = (l1, l2) in let (_,res) = List.fold_left f base args in res in
  removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2));;

  | [] -> ""

let rec sepConcat  : string -> string list -> string = fun sep sl  -> 
  match sl with
  | [] -> ""
  | h::t ->
      let f a x = h in let base = "" in let l = t in List.fold_left f base l;;
